                                <note>The book originally ended with Ch. IV.4 (III. 22), but the remainder has been added by a later hand, with a
                                subscription</note>
                                <explicit type="subscriptio">The subscription, added by the later hand, gives the name of the writer and
                                    owner, <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11392WaldaF">Walda Fāsiladas</persName>: 
                                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘ፲ወ፪፡ ደቂቀ፡ ነቢያት። ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚ' ፡
                                        ሣህሉ፡ ወምሕረቱ፡ የሃሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ገብሩ፡ ወልደ፡ ፋሲለደስ። 
                                        ዘትሣየጦ፡ በንዋዩ፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ።</foreign>
                                </explicit>
                                
                            </msItem>
                            
                            
                        </msItem>
                        
                        
                        
